==English==

===Noun===
'''androgen'''
#The generic term for any natural or synthetic compound, usually a [[steroid]] [[hormone]], that [[stimulate]]s or [[control]]s the [[development]] and maintenance of [[masculine]] characteristics in [[vertebrate]]s.   A male [[sex hormone]] such as [[testosterone]] or [[anabolic steroids]].

